version_description:
* Deviant and final weapon form filters.
* Monster sorting fixed
* Affinity and second weapon elements
* Some other small bug fixes

This app is open source! You can help make it better here: https://github.com/JoeLago/MHGUDB-iOS

* Deviant and final weapon form filters.
* Monster sorting fixed
* Affinity and second weapon elements
* Some other small bug fixes

This app is open source! You can help make it better here: https://github.com/JoeLago/MHGUDB-iOS

Happy holidays! I have a few gifts for you after an entire year of patience. If you have a moment, leave a review. Updates and features are driven by your moral support and encouragement.
- Keep track of the armor and weapons you are most interested in
